                            <comment id="13806023" author="djencks" created="Sat, 26 Oct 2013 07:41:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;rev 1535941&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I basically reversed many of the changes in felix-3651 rev 1480108 except now extracting the info we need from the Configuration before ungetting the config admin instance.  This makes the logic flow a little clearer.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13806130" author="djencks" created="Sat, 26 Oct 2013 16:30:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Pierre reports the problem is still there.  It looks like CM_LOCATION_CHANGE events are supposed to be sent out even before there are any properties set.  In rev 1536005 I added some code to ignore these events.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
